### 3. Agent Behavior Inconsistencies

**Symptoms:**
```
Agent doesn't follow expected behavior patterns
Responses don't match persona characteristics
Agent switches behavior mid-conversation
```

**Root Causes:**
- Corrupted persona configuration
- Session context interference
- Mixed agent state

**Solution:**

**Verify Persona Configuration:**
```bash
# Check persona definition files
cat {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas/developer.json
cat {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas/architect.json

# Validate JSON configuration
python3 -m json.tool {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas/developer.json

# Check for configuration corruption
find {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas/ -name "*.json" -exec python3 -m json.tool {} \; > /dev/null
```

**Reset Agent Configuration:**
```bash
# Backup current configuration
cp -r {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas.backup

# Restore default configuration
cp -r {{APM_ROOT}}/config/default/personas/* {{APM_ROOT}}/agents/personas/

# Test agent activation
/ap
/dev --test-mode
```

